ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectSand Point First Nation Reserve SETTING APART
PrecisSetting apart of 986.648 hectares (2,437.97 acres) of land, mines and minerals included, for the use and benefit of the BINGWI NEYAASHI ANISHINAABEK as Sand Point First Nation Reserve, located in the geographic township of Kilkenny, Municipality of Greenstone, Territorial District of Thunder Bay, approximately 160 kilometres northeast of the city of Thunder Bay, Ontario.
